 SPAR is giving away some amazing prizes in the SPAR Advent Calendar Competition. All you have to do is keep an eye on the special promotion in Lowvelder, snap yourself with your till slip showing your purchase of the promotional product from your local SPAR Store on the day it is advertised, and submit your picture below. You can also send your selfie to Lowvelder’s Facebook page. Simple as that! The prizes are sure to light up your Christmas spirit and include a Bosch fridge/freezer, Kenwood  food mixer, Defy tumble dryer, Samsung washing machine, Defy air conditioner, Defy washing machine, Bosch dishwasher and a Samsung component sound system. To enter fill in the form below and upload your product selfie: Unfortunately this competition ended on December 23, 2016. Be sure to visit our competition section for more great chances to win.